Arduino Port Assignments for Blimpbot

Main microprocessor is an Arduino Mega 2560

Motor control:
Digital PWM ports 2-5 (output)

LED outputs:
Digital ports 8-12

Pushbutton inputs:
Digital ports 14,15?  or analog inputs A8, A9?

Ultrasonic Sensors:
Paired digital ports (20,21) - (52,53).
Trigger on even-numbered (output), read on odd-numbered (input)

Optical Sensors:
Analog ports A0 - A7 (input)
